        <section eId="sec_12_81dd">
          <num>12-81dd</num>
          <heading>Municipal option to abate real or personal property taxes paid by a nonprofit land conservation organization</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-81dd. Municipal option to abate real or personal property taxes paid by a nonprofit land conservation organization.Any municipality may, upon approval by its legislative body, abate the real or personal property taxes due for any portion of a tax year or the interest on delinquent taxes with respect to any tax paid by a nonprofit land conservation organization that was due for a period before the date of acquisition but which was paid subsequent to the date of acquisition.
